      <title>习近平的市场调整令业内人士感到惊讶，对市场溃败表现出警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/xi-s-markets-shakeup-surprised-insiders-showing-alarm-over-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周以来，中国主要证券监管机构的工作人员一直在夜以继日地工作，寻找在爆炸发生时支撑中国暴跌股市的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/xi-s-markets-shakeup-surprised-insiders-showing-alarm-over-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 00:54:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州州长表示该州电力供应需要增长 10% 至 15%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/texas-governor-says-state-power-supply-needs-to-grow-10-to-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州州长格雷格·阿博特 (Greg Abbott) 表示，该州需要每年将供电能力提高 15%，以满足家庭和企业不断增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/texas-governor-says-state-power-supply-needs-to-grow-10-to-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 00:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚人有权在下班后忽略办公室电话和电子邮件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/australian-workers-will-get-right-to-disconnect-under-new-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚很快将效仿一些欧洲国家，赋予员工下班后断网的权利，这使得企业在员工下班后给员工打电话或发电子邮件时面临潜在的惩罚性后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/australian-workers-will-get-right-to-disconnect-under-new-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 00:01:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
