      <title>拜登称普京在乌克兰援助枯竭之际“寸步难行”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/biden-says-putin-on-balls-of-his-heels-as-ukraine-aid-dries-up</link>
