      <title>参议院投票终结边境协议前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/senate-vote-ends-border-deal-prospects-setting-election-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在前总统唐纳德·特朗普和众议院共和党领导人谴责该协议后，参议院对实施新边境限制的努力给予了致命一击，阻止了经过仔细谈判的两党妥协。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/senate-vote-ends-border-deal-prospects-setting-election-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊、汇丰银行、AT&T 共同承诺在墨西哥雇用移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/un-partners-on-business-plan-to-hire-migrants-in-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊、汇丰控股和 AT&amp;T 等 50 家公司承诺在联合国移民机构的帮助下在墨西哥雇用移民，此举旨在为数千名移民中的一些人提供就业机会。近年来在这个拉丁美洲国家定居的外国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/un-partners-on-business-plan-to-hire-migrants-in-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里约热内卢在狂欢节前几天宣布登革热卫生紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里约热内卢（美联社）——里约热内卢周一宣布，由于爆发蚊媒登革热，该市宣布进入公共卫生紧急状态，就在巴西各地狂欢节庆祝活动开始前几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</guid>
